:: crotch_7_crotch_8_3
<<nobr>>

<<speech "thalara">>Are you sure you aren‚Äôt simply afraid of being seen differently? That what‚Äôs inside won‚Äôt be taken as seriously without what once stood outside?<</speech>><br>

