:: crotch_9_crotch_10_2
<<nobr>>

<<speech "thalara">>You‚Äôve made progress. Real change. Do you understand what this reversal means?<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>It means I‚Äôm taking back something. Not because I hate where I was going. But because I‚Äôm not done being who I was.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "thalara">>That‚Äôs not weakness. It‚Äôs clarity. Every step must be owned. If you move forward too fast without belief, you fracture. And I will not let you shatter, Caelan.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>I never thought I'd want this back. The weight. The pull. But after that last session, everything felt... too quiet. Too small. I looked down and felt like I‚Äôd erased a chapter before I was ready.<</speech>><br>
[[Move Forth|crotch_9_crotch_10_3]]

<</nobr>>

:: crotch_9_crotch_10_3
<<nobr>>

<<speech "thalara">>You felt like a guest in your own skin. That is no place from which to rule or evolve.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>So this‚Äôll bring it back? Not all the way‚Ä¶ but more?<</speech>><br>

<<speech "thalara">>Yes. From where you were very large to where you once stood with pride. The potion restores what has receded. Blood will rush. Tissue will swell. Veins awaken. You‚Äôll feel heavy again, not only in body, but in presence.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>I missed that word. Presence.<</speech>><br>

[[Move Forth|crotch_9_crotch_10_4]]
<</nobr>>

:: crotch_9_crotch_10_4
<<nobr>>

<<speech "thalara">>Presence does not only come from parts, Caelan. But reclaiming them can be a declaration, if done knowingly.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>And if this becomes a cycle? Back and forth forever. Do I just keep undoing myself?<</speech>><br>

<<speech "thalara">>No. The cycle ends when you end it. Not when the potions do. If this is what brings your truth closer, then it is not regression. It‚Äôs refinement.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>My mother wouldn‚Äôt approve. She thinks every drop I take should go in the other direction.<</speech>><br>
[[Move Forth|crotch_9_crotch_10_5]]
<</nobr>>

:: crotch_9_crotch_10_5
<<nobr>>

<<speech "thalara">>Your mother sees a queen. I see a soul in flux. Only you see who you are becoming. Or should. If this reversal helps you see it more clearly, it‚Äôs worth it.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>I need this. Not forever. But today.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "thalara">>Then take it. Feel the return not of manhood, but of something you feared had vanished without your say.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>I won‚Äôt apologize for reclaiming myself.<</speech>><br>

[[Move Forth|crotch_9_crotch_10_6]]
