<<speech "mc">>Fine. Point taken.<</speech>><br>

[[Move Forth|crotch_10_crotch_9_5]]
<</nobr>>

:: crotch_10_crotch_9_5
<<nobr>>

<<speech "thalara">>This one will be warmer than before. Gentle, but undeniable. Your body will sigh away another layer. You may feel heat along the base, a hollowing in your groin. The muscle will shrink; the veins will quiet. Your form will simplify.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>Is there a point where it stops feeling like I‚Äôm losing‚Ä¶ and starts feeling like I‚Äôm becoming?<</speech>><br>

<<speech "thalara">>Yes. But no one can tell you when. It‚Äôs different for every soul.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>And what if I still don‚Äôt know if I want to be a queen?<</speech>><br>

[[Move Forth|crotch_10_crotch_9_6]]
<</nobr>>

:: crotch_10_crotch_9_6
<<nobr>>

<<speech "thalara">>Then be Caelan. Fully, fiercely. And when the crown comes, you‚Äôll know whether to wear it or cast it aside.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>Cheers to uncertainty, then.<</speech>><br>

