:: crotch_10_crotch_11_4
<<nobr>>

<<speech "thalara">>I‚Äôll grant you the form, but not the illusion. If you believe this makes you whole, drink. If you believe this makes you safe, wait. You cannot drink both destinies.<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>I‚Äôm not asking for forever. Just a moment to feel real again.<</speech>><br>

